		  <td width="3"></td>
          <td class="mainbody">

<p>
For the druids, shaman, clerics of Norrath there haven't been much to allow you to gain magical aid before. But your dieties have listened. Be sure to find a friendly intelligent companion to help you fashion the spells you need, because you can't do it yourself.
</p>
<p>
At the moment the alternate classes (Paladin, Ranger, Beastlord) that are assigned to a spell are NOT, repeat NOT to be considered Valid. These Various Spells need to be examined, based up the recipe used to produce it to verify the classes. These were entered to speed the basic entry. These spells have NOT been verified for the classes specified at this time. 5/29/2003 - Krazick
</p><br><div align="right">Last Modified By: EQTC Editor Krazick&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>

		Last Modified on: 2003-07-09 11:26:09&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</i></div><br>
